What a week! I wanted to share a few highlights from filming.. As a huge fan of the genre, I always wanted to play a role in a film like this .. and what an experience it was! I spent loooong days working on an incredible @fullmoonfeatures supernatural horror film.. ‘Bring Her To Me’ ! Thank you to @zatoichix1 @realcharlesband for casting me as Mara and trusting me to deliver on your vision! Brooks you made it such a collaborative and fun work environment and brought such a great team of people together. My fellow cast were all SO talented and so fun to work with! We had so many laughs and delirious late nights together .. and I can’t imagine going through it with anyone else! @kalond_irlanda @rosgentle @emersonniemchick you all killed it! The crew were equally wonderful! Shout out to @howwex12 @matt_leal_ thank you for making me feel so comfortable and at ease in every scene! @alexys.pao thank you for making me beautiful everyday! And for being my vegan army lol @miasaigeartistry thank you for stepping in on our final day and getting us across the finish line!  @mbaskinn you were always on point and brought the best energy! @rickmayelian sound extraordinaire - you have the patience of a saint! Lol so many amazing people and new friendships forged! Big thanks to my agent @sovereigntalentgroupinc also! And Nancy McManus casting! 

I can not wait to share “Bring Her To Me” with you all!! Stay tuned!! It’s going to be a fun one!! 💀👻

It’s been a somewhat tumultuous year, and due to that I lost any semblance of a workout routine.. but I’m back! Ready to focus on my health and fitness.. and what better way than to start my fitness journey than with one of the absolute best @itsmannyh at @apollogym in Glendale! We began our sessions with a health and fitness assessment.. 😱 followed by an incredible first training session.. AND finished with a recovery sports massage!  My overall goal is to tone up and improve my fitness and Im excited to share my progress as our sessions continue! I love working out but find it difficult to self motivate so this was the perfect solution for me! With an incredible set-up, top of the line equipment and a trainer @itsmannyh who is not only extremely knowledgeable but is also committed to his clients and their fitness goals, Apollo Gym is a must! 

** Your initial Health and fitness assessment with Manny is complimentary.. So there is absolutely no reason not to take control of your body goals, check out @apollogym and see if it’s a good fit for you! 💪

Wish me luck! 🍀💋
